summaries.short: Esme and Roy help Hugo and Fig learn to share; plus, Esme and Roy show Simon something as amazing as his favorite TV show: the outdoors.
summaries.full: When Hugo and Fig don't want to share their Monster Sitters, Esme and Roy need to get creative and teach them how to take turns. Plus, Simon has watched enough of his favorite TV show, so Esme and Roy take him outside. But will they be able to find anything more amazing than his show?

summaries.short: Tillie is having a no-good, rotten day - she's got a case of the Ickies; plus, Tillie starts to see things in the dark.
summaries.full: Tillie is having a no-good, rotten day - she's got a case of the Ickies! Now, it's up to Esme and Roy to find the cure. Plus, Esme and Roy are tucking Tillie in for bed, but when they turn out the lights, Tillie starts to see things in the dark.

summaries.short: Snugs has a bad case of the Sneezles and needs to rest in bed, but he has a hard time staying put. Plus, it's Simon's first time at the beach and Esme and Roy want to show him a great time, but everything keeps going wrong.

summaries.short: The Monster Sitters take Fig to a birthday party, but she won't let go of the present; plus, Esme and Roy teach Baby Fig to ask for help.
summaries.full: The Monster Sitters take Fig to a birthday party, but she won't let go of the present. Now, it's up to them to teach Fig the joys of giving. Plus, when Baby Fig wants to do everything herself, Esme and Roy need to teach her that it's okay to ask for help.

summaries.short: Hugo, Tillie and Simon go to Monster Sitters' HQ for a dance party; plus, Tillie needs to clean up before she can play with her new truck.
summaries.full: Hugo, Tillie and Simon go to Monster Sitters' HQ for a dance party. Every time Simon tries to dance like his friends, though, his arms start to wiggle and get in the way. Plus, Esme and Roy are watching Tillie. Mr. Plink tells them that Tillie needs to clean up her blocks in the backyard before she can play with her new truck, but she keeps getting distracted.
